        <mxCell id="2eJlH5tE73RZIXNoKa9L-182" value="&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font&gt;Name:&amp;nbsp;ksm-posstg-lmd-function-split-txt-by-sent-time&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font&gt;Parameters:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;・&lt;/span&gt;Created manifest path:&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;˜/pos-master/ishida/csv/{store_code}/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;・Manifest file name:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;{store_code 4char}{00}{date_time 16char}ESLDATA.TXT.manifest&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;Process:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;・Merged path 0000 file&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;・Divide to TXT file with sent date_time in end of file name&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;　・&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;{store_code 4char}{00}{date_time 16char}ESLDATA.TXT&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;　・If already file with same sent date_time, add the data below the exsit file&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;・With new TXT created, add the schedule for sent the file&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;　・Schedule